%% view: VIEW-DEPLOYMENT (deployment)
N_EKS_PAYMENTS_PROD_EKS["payments-prod-eks"]:::cluster
N_CONT_CHECKOUT_API["Checkout API"]:::container
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE["Payment Engine"]:::container
N_CONT_RISK_SCORER["Risk Scorer"]:::container
N_ENV_PROD["prod"]:::environment
N_EXT_BANK_GW[["Bank Gateway"]]:::external
N_FLUXKUS_PAYMENTS_APPS["payments-apps"]:::flux
N_GITSRC_PAYMENTS_SAMPLE_SOURCE["payments-sample-source"]:::source
N_HELMREL_CHECKOUT_API["checkout-api"]:::helm
N_HELMREL_PAYMENT_ENGINE["payment-engine"]:::helm
N_HELMREL_RISK_SCORER["risk-scorer"]:::helm
N_NS_FLUX_SYSTEM["flux-system"]:::namespace
N_NS_PAYMENTS["payments"]:::namespace
N_NS_RISK["risk"]:::namespace
N_ACT_SUPPORT(("Support Agent")):::person
N_CONT_CHECKOUT_API -->|depends_on: Delegates payment authorization. catalog: payment authorization is requested, checkout is active| N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on: Sends high-risk review notification. catalog: support agent is notified, payment review is pending, support agent| N_ACT_SUPPORT
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on: Returns decline outcome for customer messaging. catalog: payment is declined, decline reason| N_CONT_CHECKOUT_API
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on: Returns temporary unavailable response when bank link is down. catalog: bank link is unavailable| N_CONT_CHECKOUT_API
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on: Requests fraud scoring. catalog: fraud check is enabled, risk score is high, risk score| N_CONT_RISK_SCORER
N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on: Calls bank authorization API. catalog: bank link is available, payment authorization is requested| N_EXT_BANK_GW
N_EKS_PAYMENTS_PROD_EKS -->|part_of| N_ENV_PROD
N_FLUXKUS_PAYMENTS_APPS -->|depends_on source| N_GITSRC_PAYMENTS_SAMPLE_SOURCE
N_FLUXKUS_PAYMENTS_APPS -->|manages| N_HELMREL_CHECKOUT_API
N_FLUXKUS_PAYMENTS_APPS -->|manages| N_HELMREL_PAYMENT_ENGINE
N_FLUXKUS_PAYMENTS_APPS -->|manages| N_HELMREL_RISK_SCORER
N_FLUXKUS_PAYMENTS_APPS -->|runs_in| N_NS_FLUX_SYSTEM
N_HELMREL_CHECKOUT_API -->|deploys| N_CONT_CHECKOUT_API
N_HELMREL_CHECKOUT_API -->|depends_on source| N_GITSRC_PAYMENTS_SAMPLE_SOURCE
N_HELMREL_CHECKOUT_API -->|runs_in| N_NS_PAYMENTS
N_HELMREL_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|deploys| N_CONT_PAYMENT_ENGINE
N_HELMREL_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|depends_on source| N_GITSRC_PAYMENTS_SAMPLE_SOURCE
N_HELMREL_PAYMENT_ENGINE -->|runs_in| N_NS_PAYMENTS
N_HELMREL_RISK_SCORER -->|deploys| N_CONT_RISK_SCORER
N_HELMREL_RISK_SCORER -->|depends_on source| N_GITSRC_PAYMENTS_SAMPLE_SOURCE
N_HELMREL_RISK_SCORER -->|runs_in| N_NS_RISK
N_NS_FLUX_SYSTEM -->|part_of| N_EKS_PAYMENTS_PROD_EKS
N_NS_PAYMENTS -->|part_of| N_EKS_PAYMENTS_PROD_EKS
N_NS_RISK -->|part_of| N_EKS_PAYMENTS_PROD_EKS
